{
  "title": "Gently Spiced Syrian Chicken Kebabs",
  "description": "A light and bitter Syrian dish featuring fajita seasoning, perfect for a post-workout meal, with an ayurvedic-tamasic friendly twist.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
