  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, ginger, fajita seasoning, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken to the marinade and mix well to coat.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread the marinated chicken onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Let the kebabs rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley or cilantro if desired."
  ],
